例如：
    string str="this is a very good day!"


stringstream：
    ``` 
    string str="this is a good day!"
    stringstream ss(str)//string->字符流
    while(getline(ss,tmp," "))//分隔符可以设置为其他分隔符
        cout<<tmp<<endl;
    ```

istringstream:
    ```
    string str="this is a good day!"
    istringstream ss(s);
    while(ss>>line)//分离空格分开的字符串
        cout<<line<<endl;
    ```